{"tid":1633770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚多鬼叫人唔好裝修","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:35.000Z","uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eac88c80ebc974795a76cef4e1e7526e10a144c2","tid":1633770,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b41cac35adc903b5efdaeac84934044b4c5939","tid":1633770,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落，兩邊一齊做唔撚得？"},{"pid":"0d45a6674cb677983dcb3efaf19d6f6a86f13c28","tid":1633770,"uid":205449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"真 連登好撚多風向撚<br />\n唔該大家用下個腦分析下 咪信足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5245319627c342dfc06aa2f7323cc99b74ed4cc7","tid":1633770,"uid":135697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"688d19c6fb88522d3a7b35c8055ac696c18a229a","tid":1633770,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"擺明裝修依個方向係正確先咁多五毛出嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你搞著班商家佬佢重唔屌柒政府呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地奶共都係求財 家陣畀人裝修蝕錢咪唔再奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d2121f98